    <h1>My account is hacked</h1>
    <div>
        <p>If you believe that someone is using your account please report this immediately to the systems administrator to prevent damage to the data and system at large. The following signs might give you clues that someone hacked your account.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <p><b>Marks manupulation.</b> By default lecturers are only allowed to change marks and the lecturer who created a profile is the only one authorised to make changes to the profile. If you notice that marks are being changed even though you are not the one changing them report this immediately to the system administrator </p>
            </li>

            <li>
                <p><b>Student addition. </b>Students are added to the profile by the Lecturer, if you notice student being added without you doing it</p>
